	The definite discography of the most aggressive hardcore band
	that Sweden ever produced. Mob 47 had the same impact in Europe
	that Siege did in USA, or Gauze in Japan. This complete reissue
	pack contains their rare first demo tape "Hardcore Attack",
	plus the EP tracks, cover versions, live and compilation
	tracks, solo projects and much more. Special liner notes by
	Kawakami (Disclose) himself. A double CD showing you why
	Swedish Hardcore is still so mandatory until today.
